directions: South bound side of Route 18 mid way between Route 9 and the NJ Turnpike.
comment: Monday - Saturday 10AM - 9:30PM.  Sunday 11AM - 6PM.  This is a family restroom and it is kept locked at all times.  You must obtain a key from the Customer Service booth which is located in the middle of the main aisle. Just walk up and ask for the key, have had no problems.
